    <span class="eyebrow">What we do</span>
    <h1>Activities</h1>
    <p class="page-lead">
      Beyond the Annual Conference, EISS runs and partners on multi-year activities that
      address specific themes in European security studies, from training the next generation of
      scholars to assessing strategic risks to the EU.
    </p>
  </div>
</header>

